&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a combined role of Ward Clerk and House keeper on ward 117/The Infectious Diseases Unit at the Royal Stoke University Hospital. The Infectious Diseases Unit is a 14 bedded inpatient facility providing treatment for a range of clinical infections.. This post is full time 37.5 and will involve clerical duties, stock management will also have patient contact integral to the role.The ideal applicant will have excellent communication skills, a genuine interest in the area of infectious diseases and a willingness to develop their skills in this new role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
